---------------------+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+----+----+-----+-----+------+----+-----+----+-----+----+----+----+----+
     | T   | Boolean |  V  |  V  |  V  |  V  |  V  |  V  | X  | V  |  V  |  V  |  X   | X  |  X  | V  |  V  | V  | P5 | X  | X  |
     |     | Others  |  V  |  V  |  P5 |  P5 |  P5 |  P5 | X  | V  |  V  |  V  |  X   | X  |  X  | V  |  P4 | P1 | P5 | X  | X  |
BDDs +---------------+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+----+----+-----+-----+------+----+-----+----+-----+----+----+----+----+
     | EV            |  P1 |  P1 |  X  |  X  |  X  |  X  | X  | V  |  V  |  P3 |  X   | X  |  X  | P1 |  P4 | P1 | X  | X  | X  |
---------------------+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+----+----+-----+-----+------+----+-----+----+-----+----+----+----+----+
     | T   | Boolean |  V  |  V  |  X  |  X  |  X  |  X  | V  | V  |  X  |  X  |  P3  | P3 |  P3 | V  |  V  | V  | V  | V  | V  |
     |     | Others  |  V  |  V  |  X  |  X  |  X  |  X  | P5 | V  |  X  |  X  |  P3  | P3 |  P3 | V  |  P4 | P1 | P5 | P5 | P5 |
MXDs +---------------+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+----+----+-----+-----+------+----+-----+----+-----+----+----+----+----+
     | EV            |  P1 |  P1 |  X  |  X  |  X  |  X  | X  | P1 |  P2 |  X  |  P3  | P3 |  P3 | P1 |  P4 | P1 | X  | X  | X  |
=================================================================================================================================
[X]: illegal and won't be implemented; [V]: legal and implemented;
[P(1-5)]: legal but not implemented (with priority number, the smaller the higher priority)

